Package: batchpkginstall
Title: Automated Installation, Loading or Uninstallation of R Packages in Source File
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lexun", "Yu", , "lyu@prpr.one", role = c("aut", "cre")
           )
Description: This package provides automated management for install, load and uninstall R packages specified in library() functions within the headers of source files. It detects the packages listed, checks whether they are installed, and offers prompts to install, load, or uninstall them in bulk. 
License: use_mit_license()
Encoding: UTF-8
